description: To Perform end to end Verification Flow
name: End to End Verification Flow

elements.name: Validate the verification flow with the selected country and document type for a user.

steps.name: I am on Home Page
Enter value in Session Language as "English"
Enter value in Document Country as "India"
Enter value in Document Type as "Passport"
Select value in Verification Type as "Redirect"
Click on VeriffMe button
Click on Continue with your current device button
Verify the link text displayed on the Start Session Page
Click on Start Session button
Verify the link text displayed on the User New Session Page for "Passport"
Click on Continue button
User is ready to take photo
